t l’influence du verre sur divers aspects de notre vie et de notre culture.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aSCIENCE / Physics / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-3178-440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759831784423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759831784/original  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles